{"name":"Ophelia Berendsen","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"","alignment":"","hitDice":"10","armorName":"other","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"19 (natural armor, bracers of defense)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":true,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"73 (10d6 + 28)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"10","dexPoints":"16","conPoints":"13","intPoints":"16","wisPoints":"14","chaPoints":"20","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"10","customCr":"12 (8,400 XP)","customProf":4,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The archmage can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The archmage regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the archmage can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the archmage can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The archmage can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the archmage's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the archmage's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the archmage dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON] is an 14th-level spellcaster. Her spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC [CHA SAVE], [CHA ATK] to hit with spell attacks). [MON] can cast _Charm Person_ and _Detect thoughts_ at will and has the following sorcerer spells prepared:\n\n\n> * Cantrips (at will): _ray of frost, dancing lights, mage hand, prestidigitation, shocking grasp_\n> * 1st level (4 slots): _detect magic, identify, shield, ice knife_\n> * 2nd level (3 slots): _detect thoughts, mirror image, misty step_\n> * 3rd level (3 slots): _counterspell, major image, slow_\n> * 4th level (3 slots): _greater invisibility, dimension door, stoneskin_\n> * 5th level (2 slots): _summon **Erz Agrious**, dominate person, seeming_\n> * 6th level (1 slot): _Otiluke's freezing sphere_\n> * 7th level (1 slot): _etherealness_"},{"name":"Metamagic (10/day)","desc":"[MON] has access to the following metamagic options:\n- Heightened Spell\n- Twinned Spell\n- Subtle Spell"},{"name":"Ice affinity","desc":"[MON] adds her proficiency bonus to damage rolls which do cold damage."},{"name":"Shared Resistances","desc":"While _Erz Agrious_ is summoned, [MON] has shared resistance to one of Erz's damage types. Additionally, she gains [2d4] temporary hit points every time Erz takes damage as she's surrounded in a wall of blue sparks."},{"name":"Masked Ablate","desc":"[MON] is bound to a Masked Ablate. [MON] can telepathically call the Ablate to travel to it. If the Ablate is within 60 feet of [MON], half of any damage she takes (rounded up) is transferred to the Ablate."},{"name":"Bracers of Defense","desc":"[MON] has +2 to AC."},{"name":"Stoic's Ring","desc":"[MON] has advnatage on Wisdom saving throws"}],"actions":[{"name":"Claw","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft, one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1d4] piercing damage."},{"name":"Stoic's Ring","desc":"[MON] ends one frightened or charmed condition."},{"name":"Ring of Pain (1/day)","desc":"[MON] may take [2d8] necrotic damage to cast _Power word: pain_ on one creature. [MON] takes another [1d8] necrotic damage each round the creature is affected by the spell. Any creature attempting to attune to this spell also suffers _Power word: pain_."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Heels of Hasty Retreat (1/Day)","desc":"[MON] clicks her heels together. Every creature within 20 ft must make a DC 15 strength saving throw or be pushed 15 feed back. [MON] may then immediately use her reaction to cast a spell targeting only herself. _These crystal shoes have a slight heel to them, so as to blend in with polite society._"}],"reactions":[{"name":"Counterspell","desc":"[MON] casts _counterspell_."},{"name":"Shield","desc":"[MON] casts _shield_."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"int","order":3},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int"},{"name":"deception","stat":"cha","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"history","stat":"int"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"cold","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"specialdamage":[{"name":"Stoneskin: Bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical attacks","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"Stoneskin: Bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical attacks (Resistant)","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Aire","speaks":true},{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":true},{"name":"Halfling","speaks":true},{"name":"Thieves' Cant","speaks":true},{"name":"Undercommon","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Ophelia","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}